==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Unfrequent
<hw>Un`fre*quent"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>frequent</ets>.]</ety> <def>To cease to
frequent.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>They quit their thefts and <qex>unfrequent</qex> the fields.</q>
<rj><qau>J. Philips.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

